				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{INC}}_{{\mathrm{baseline}}} \ast {\mathrm{OR}}_{{\mathrm{dnSNV}}}^2$$\end{document}INCbaseline*ORdnSNV2

Following this logic, the disease incidence in the population of individuals carrying n dnSNVs would be \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
